The paper discusses active learning in the context of deep learning and image data, which suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories. "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) is the most likely category, as the paper deals with active learning, a subfield of machine learning. "cs.CV" (Computer Vision) is also highly likely, as the paper specifically focuses on image data. "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are also possible categories, as the paper deals with deep learning techniques. Finally, "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) is a less likely category, but still possible, as the paper discusses the use of deep learning for skin cancer diagnosis from lesion images.
